videos.description: Off the Stephanie Jones steal, Sarah Myers finds Kaila Charles for an easy layup to cut the deficit for Maryland.
videos.headline: Myers to Charles closes the gap of Maryland

videos.description: Tyasha Harris drives the length of the floor for a right-handed layup to push the lead to 19 for the Gamecocks.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_Final Game Highlight South Carolina (Harris goes coast-to-coast for a South Carolina bucket) 2017/11/13

videos.headline: Harris goes coast-to-coast for a South Carolina bucket

videos.description: Mikiah Herbert Harrigan score on an easy right-handed layup to pad the lead for South Carolina.
videos.headline: Harrigan scores in transition for South Carolina

videos.description: South Carolina head coach Dawn Staley and star Aj'a Wilson talk about Wilson's career-high 32-point performance and the team's overall effort in victory over Maryland.
videos.headline: Wilson's career high leads South Carolina to a big road win

videos.description: A'ja Wilson's 32 points lead the way in No. 4 South Carolina's 94-86 win against No. 15 Maryland.
videos.headline: South Carolina holds off Maryland's late rally
